{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"130209d7-5419-48dd-bf9a-ec393634a7b7","content":"For NativeAOT apps, the CLR's built-in crash dump mechanism isn't available — you must point `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` to your `createdump` binary explicitly. Here's the pod spec changes:\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Pod\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: my-app\n      # ... your existing image/ports/etc ...\n      env:\n        # Enable automatic crash dump on unhandled exceptions / crashes\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n          value: \"1\"\n        # Dump type: 1=Normal, 2=WithHeap, 3=Triage, 4=Full\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n          value: \"2\"\n        # Path to createdump (required for NativeAOT — no runtime dir)\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n          value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n        # Dump output path (%d = PID, %t = timestamp)\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n          value: \"/tmp/dumps/coredump.%d.%t.dmp\"\n        # Optional: enable diagnostics for troubleshooting dump creation\n        - name: DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics\n          value: \"1\"\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: dump-volume\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n  volumes:\n    - name: dump-volume\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- **`DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`** is critical for NativeAOT since there's no runtime directory to discover `createdump` automatically.\n- **`DbgMiniDumpType: 2`** (WithHeap) gives you managed + native heap — good balance of size vs. debuggability. Use `4` (Full) if you need everything.\n- **`emptyDir`** works for transient collection. Swap for a **PersistentVolumeClaim** if you need dumps to survive pod restarts.\n- Ensure `createdump` has execute permissions and the process has `SYS_PTRACE` capability if your security context restricts it:\n\n```yaml\n      securityContext:\n        capabilities:\n          add: [\"SYS_PTRACE\"]\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1b8e1296-1461-4468-8271-7fd827fc782a","outputTokens":585,"requestId":"DA05:1837D6:51DFD8:5D9EE3:6A03D873"},"id":"6ca9cbe2-fcc5-4ac8-8e34-eb08e4ac20f5","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:48:47.655Z","parentId":"bca043ad-e8d9-4275-a268-a1e905da4d7b"}
